p: Mass spectral data obtained from the orbitrap MS were processed using Xcalibur 3.1 with Foundation 3.1 (Thermo Fisher Scientific). Compounds were tentatively identified by matching their exact (calculated) masses of protonated (M + H) adducts with measured m/z values and PSI-MS/MS fragmentation patterns from the in-house MS/MS database, and online databases such as the Human Metabolome Database [ 15] and METLIN [ 16], and the literature. The compound structures were drawn using ChemDraw Professional 15.0 (PerkinElmer, Waltham, MA, USA).
